<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><span class="location-text"><strong>Been on a 18/19 Inghams ski holiday?</strong></span></p>
<p><span class="location-text"><strong>Receive £50 per couple off your next holiday with Inghams Italy and Lakes &amp; Mountains, or £50 per person discount when you book with our sister company, Explore.</strong></span></p>
<p><br /><strong>Simply quote your 18/19 Inghams Ski booking reference to receive your discount off either a Italy, Lakes &amp; Mountains holiday or an Explore holiday. </strong></p>
<p> </p>
<div style="font-size: small;">
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Not combinable with any other offer</li>
<li>Offer applies to bookings made from 27 June 2018 to 31 May 2019</li>
<li>Booking references will be verified</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
